videoDetails.Title: I personally removed ALL CAS from War Thunder!
videoDetails.Description:
DOLALRplays War Thunder  G6 Rhino  gameplay. 

Today we're back playing  with South African G6 Rhino in War Thunder ground realistic battles.
G6 is probably one of the most fun vehicles in the game right now. It has 155mm gun with an amazing HEVT round(which is pretty good for removing planes from the sky) , high elevating gun, and decent mobility. Overall amazing vehicle for 7.0. 

G6 Rhino is a perfect tool when you're  depressed for being  destroyed by CAS all day. 
You can call it antidepressant of War Thunder.

So today we're going to to remove all CAS from ground realistic battles . Enjoy ;)

G6 PART 1 https://youtu.be/OIFlvVY6M5o
